name: Sic et vos;
office-part: Antiphona;
mode: 8;
book: Antiphonale Romanum II, 2009, p. 382;
transcriber: Innocent Smith, op;
commentary: Lc 17, 10;
text: Tell yourselves: We are useless servants, for we did only what we should have done.;
